                " fractional independent yield, it needs the mass yield,",
                " which were obtained from the cumulative yield measured",
                " by author and other published cumulative yield.",
                "In this subentry, for Br-82, the fractional independent",
                " yield (1.3+-0.3) x 10**(-4) was larger than the",
                " independent yield (7.5+-1.7)x 10**(-5) presented in",
                " above subentry (32634003).this seems unreasonable,so",
                " one of these two values should Be wrong. Unfortunately",
                " the compiler cannot contact with authors, so users",
                " should be careful when use the values for Br-82."
